# Choosy – Safety Standards

Choosy is committed to providing a safe and respectful environment for all users.

## Our Commitment

We do not tolerate:

* Harassment or bullying
* Hate speech or abusive content
* Sexual or explicit content
* Content involving minors in inappropriate ways
* Spam or misleading content

## User Responsibility

Users are responsible for the content they create, including polls, comments, and interactions.

## Reporting & Action

If you encounter any inappropriate or harmful content, you can:

* Report it within the app (if available)
* Contact us directly via email

We review reports and take appropriate action, including:

* Content removal
* Account suspension or permanent ban

## Child Safety

Choosy is intended for users aged 13 and above.
We strictly prohibit any content that exploits or harms minors.

